threads.title: A1990 (820-01814-01) not powering on, only 5V on USB
threads.message:
Hi there,

I have an A1990 (820-01814-01) not powering on.

On all 4 USB ports I only get 5V and around 100 to 200 mA.
(yes I know this is not accurate, but I only have one number after the decimal point at the moment)

On PPBUS_G3H I get 12.27V

What to check next?

Thanks in advance
